posting_body: ['For a LIMITED TIME ONLY, Fall into Savings at Solhaus-- Lease your fall home today and receive $100 off monthly!', '-Study lounge with print station', '-Central A/C', '-Nest Thermostat', '-In Unit Laundry', '-Electronic Key Entry', '-Dishwasher', '-24/7 Fitness Center', '-Walk in Closets', '-Wheel Chair Accessible', '- Free Wi-Fi in Amenity Spaces', '-Surface Lot Parking', '-Street Parking -Metro Transit Access', '-Elevator', '-On-site Management', 'With one foot in Minneapolis and the other on the border of Saint Paul, Solhaus offers you the best of both worlds!', 'Our chic modern design embraces the latest in eco-friendly features such as a white membrane roof for energy efficiency, a passive solar design with large windows for natural lighting, recycling, and onsite composting.', 'Choose from our large selection of renovated pet friendly floor plans with your choice of studio, one, and two-bedroom options that include complimentary internet, in-home washers and dryers, and fully equipped kitchens with granite countertops!', 'Community amenities include a 24-hour fitness center, rooftop lounge, and parcel pending locker system.', 'Contact us today for a personalized tour and see why our residents love calling Solhaus home!']
